INCENYE 9 Khontani Jehova Njengemndeni ‘Khontani Loyo lowadala lizulu nemhlaba.’ Njengobe ufundzile kulencwajana, liBhayibheli licuketse timiso letinyenti letitawusita wena nemndeni wakho. Jehova ufuna kutsi ujabule. Wetsembisa kutsi nangabe ukubeka kucala kukhonta yena, ‘tonkhe leletinye tintfo utawengetelwa tona.’ (Matewu 6:33) Ufuna kutsi ube ngumngani wakhe sibili. Wasebentise onkhe ematfuba kute ukhulise bungani bakho naNkulunkulu. Leli lilungelo lelikhulu kakhulu umuntfu langase abe nalo. 
..........
) Zindla ngaloko lokufundzako. (Tihlabelelo 77:11, 12) Kulalela Nkulunkulu kuphindze kufake ekhatsi kuya njalo emihlanganweni yebuKhristu. Kukhuluma nalabanye ngaJehova kungulenye indlela lebalulekile yekucinisa buhlobo bakho naye. Nawuchubeka ukwenta loko, utawusondzelana kakhulu naye. LONGAKWENTA: Tibekele sikhatsi sekufundza liBhayibheli malanga onkhe futsi uthantaze Njengemndeni, kufanele nibeke tintfo letiphatselene nebuhlobo benu naNkulunkulu kucala kunekutijabulisa kanye nekuphumula 2 KUJ
